message.body: Hey Dan! No I haven't found a couch but my host mom is picking me up. Although I thought she doesn't have time... I just saw your pictures and it's so funny that I also know Lisa from the Netherlands! Did she couchsurf with you? Cheers Annika
Yeah she did. Does that mean u don't need a place to stay then?
Ohok :( too bad u didn't get to visit Philly
Oh never say never :) I might be back
Well Ur welcome to stay if u need a place
Thank you! I'll let you know!
